<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{alertTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
        }
        
        .header.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #b45309 100%);
        }
        
        .header.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
        }
        
        .header.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .alert-card {
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        
        .alert-card.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
            border-left-color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        .alert-card.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffbeb 0%, #fef3c7 100%);
            border-left-color: #d97706;
        }
        
        .alert-card.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
            border-left-color: #059669;
        }
        
        .alert-card.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
            border-left-color: #2563eb;
        }
        
        .alert-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .alert-title.error {
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        
        .alert-title.warning {
            color: #92400e;
        }
        
        .alert-title.success {
            color: #065f46;
        }
        
        .alert-title.info {
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .alert-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .alert-message.error {
            color: #7f1d1d;
        }
        
        .alert-message.warning {
            color: #78350f;
        }
        
        .alert-message.success {
            color: #064e3b;
        }
        
        .alert-message.info {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .timestamp {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #b45309 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .alert-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .alert-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .alert-icon {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{alertType}}">
            <h1>System Alert</h1>
            <p>{{alertTitle}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            {{#if recipientName}}
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{recipientName}},
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="alert-card {{alertType}}">
                <div class="alert-icon">
                    {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}üö®{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'warning'}}‚ö†Ô∏è{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'success'}}‚úÖ{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'info'}}‚ÑπÔ∏è{{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="alert-title {{alertType}}">
                    {{alertTitle}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="alert-message {{alertType}}">
                    {{alertMessage}}
                </div>
                
                {{#if actionUrl}}
                <div class="cta-section">
                    <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button {{alertType}}">
                        {{#if actionText}}{{actionText}}{{else}}Learn More{{/if}}
                    </a>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="timestamp">
                <strong>Time:</strong> {{formatDate timestamp 'long'}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
                We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. Our team is working to resolve this issue as quickly as possible. If you need immediate assistance, please contact our support team.
                {{else if eq alertType 'warning'}}
                Please take note of this important information and plan accordingly. If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
                {{else if eq alertType 'success'}}
                Thank you for your attention to this matter. We appreciate your understanding and continued use of our platform.
                {{else}}
                This is an informational notice to keep you updated about our platform. No action is required on your part at this time.
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
            <div class="message">
                <strong>What you can do:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Check our status page for real-time updates</li>
                    <li>Try refreshing the page or logging out and back in</li>
                    <li>Contact support if the issue persists</li>
                    <li>Follow our social media for the latest updates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{companyName}} System Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 